    dc:creator "Archangelsky, Miguel; Brand, Cecilia" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Luchoelmis Spangler & Staines (Coleoptera: Elmidae) from Argentina and its probable larva" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226679>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226680>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226681> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226679>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Adults of Luchoelmis: 1) habitus of L. kapenkemkensis; 2) abdominal ventrites of L. kapenkemkensis; 3) lateral view of L. kapenkemkensis; 4) habitus of L. cekalovici; 5) abdominal ventrites of L. cekalovici. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226679/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226680>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 8. Male genitalia of Luchoelmis spp: 6) aedeagus of L. kapenkemkensis; 7) detail of median lobe of L. kapenkemkensis; 8) aedeagus of L. cekalovici. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226680/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226681>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 11. Male genitalia of Luchoelmis spp: 9) edeagus of L. aequalis; 10) edeagus of L. penai; 11) edeagus of L. magallanensis. (modified after Spangler & Staines 2002). Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226681/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

